<br>
But there are also a lot of gnome clerics, halfling fighters and erudite paladins too.  Pick what you want to play and once you get up to &quot;grouping age&quot; you'll be able to find groups if you look.<br>
<br>
You still want advice on a race/class to play?<br>
<br>
Troll Shadowknight.<br>
<br>
Why?  Because it was the complete opposite to that which you said you wanted to play, and I'm feeling contrary today.<br>
